WEBVTT

00:49.560 --> 00:50.200
Xu Xiao,

00:51.160 --> 00:52.560
who are you grouped with?

00:54.520 --> 00:55.120
Teacher,

00:58.600 --> 00:58.960
I...

00:59.560 --> 01:01.290
want to be grouped with Xu Xiao.

01:04.959 --> 01:05.760
Speak louder.

01:06.080 --> 01:08.080
I want to be grouped with Xu Xiao.

01:10.280 --> 01:10.800
Xu Xiao,

01:11.520 --> 01:12.520
what do you think?

01:13.680 --> 01:15.560
Okay, we will follow these groups

01:15.560 --> 01:17.620
and start the next round of learning.

01:22.760 --> 01:23.560
Zhao Xiaocen.

01:25.640 --> 01:27.360
I couldn't tell you were so two-faced.

01:27.360 --> 01:28.960
Didn't we agree at dinner last time

01:28.960 --> 01:30.960
that Lin Yuexin would team up with Xu Xiao?

01:30.960 --> 01:32.200
What was wrong with you this morning?

01:32.200 --> 01:33.240
You couldn't wait to jump out

01:33.240 --> 01:34.320
and act so passive-aggressive.

01:34.320 --> 01:34.920
No.

01:35.960 --> 01:37.840
It's because I was too anxious.

01:38.080 --> 01:39.240
What were you anxious about?

01:39.240 --> 01:40.520
Afraid someone would take your spot?

01:40.520 --> 01:41.880
It's because Xu Xiao...

01:42.640 --> 01:43.560
is right here.

01:44.240 --> 01:44.970
He's coming.

01:46.039 --> 01:46.720
I'm sorry.

01:47.120 --> 01:48.520
I don't know what to say.

01:49.640 --> 01:51.700
You're not even pretending anymore.

01:51.880 --> 01:53.120
Yan Xue, don't be mad.

01:53.560 --> 01:54.960
I'll apologize to Yuexin later.

01:54.960 --> 01:56.289
Who needs your apology?

01:56.880 --> 01:57.560
Yan Xue,

01:58.680 --> 02:00.010
what are you doing here?

02:01.160 --> 02:03.090
I don't know what I'm doing either.

02:03.120 --> 02:03.800
Yan Xue.

02:07.720 --> 02:08.250
Let's go.

02:18.320 --> 02:19.120
What's wrong?

02:19.440 --> 02:19.970
Nothing.

02:23.120 --> 02:24.520
Wu Jing, didn't you want to go shopping?

02:24.520 --> 02:25.240
I'll go with you.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.120
I don't want to.

02:26.120 --> 02:27.560
Yes, you do. Let's go.

02:27.680 --> 02:29.610
I promised to go with you last time.

02:30.640 --> 02:32.800
Yan Xue, it's just teaming up.

02:32.800 --> 02:35.260
Don't talk about Xiaocen like that anymore.

02:36.280 --> 02:37.040
No,

02:37.280 --> 02:38.280
what do you mean?

02:38.400 --> 02:40.560
Now you're making it seem like I'm bullying her.

02:40.560 --> 02:41.720
No, I didn't.

02:41.720 --> 02:42.440
Yuexin,

02:42.600 --> 02:43.680
what makes me angry is that

02:43.680 --> 02:45.360
we treat Zhao Xiaocen as a friend,

02:45.360 --> 02:46.800
but she's two-faced.

02:47.240 --> 02:48.360
Didn't she say at dinner that day

02:48.360 --> 02:49.480
she didn't like Xu Xiao?

02:49.480 --> 02:50.560
Didn't you tell me last time

02:50.560 --> 02:52.120
you were interested in Xu Xiao?

02:52.120 --> 02:53.360
That's why I helped you.

02:53.360 --> 02:55.120
She also tacitly agreed to let you team up with Xu Xiao.

02:55.120 --> 02:57.480
So now you're siding with her to lecture me?

02:57.480 --> 02:59.010
Shouldn't I be speechless?

02:59.120 --> 03:00.280
Yan Xue, don't be mad.

03:00.280 --> 03:01.600
I know you mean well,

03:02.120 --> 03:03.580
but Xiaocen means no harm.

03:04.120 --> 03:06.560
No, I'm not mad at you.

03:06.560 --> 03:08.400
I just think you are too kind.

03:08.440 --> 03:09.760
You are too much of a pushover.

03:09.760 --> 03:11.280
I just can't stand seeing others taking advantage of you.

03:11.280 --> 03:12.610
That's why I helped you.

03:13.120 --> 03:13.800
Forget it.

03:14.080 --> 03:15.160
You are not wrong about this.

03:15.160 --> 03:15.760
She is not wrong either.

03:15.760 --> 03:17.090
It's all my fault, okay?

03:17.320 --> 03:18.400
Let me calm down for a bit.

03:18.400 --> 03:18.920
Let me calm down.

03:18.920 --> 03:19.280
No.

03:19.280 --> 03:20.140
Leave me alone.

03:42.079 --> 03:42.880
Yuexin.

03:44.640 --> 03:45.400
I'm sorry.

03:46.480 --> 03:48.200
I didn't consider

03:48.920 --> 03:50.600
your feelings today.

03:53.120 --> 03:53.560
I...

03:56.280 --> 03:58.040
It's not actually that

03:59.560 --> 04:00.960
I like Xu Xiao,

04:01.800 --> 04:02.480
but rather,

04:06.600 --> 04:08.800
I didn't want him to ignore me

04:11.360 --> 04:13.360
and lose a friend like him.

04:14.960 --> 04:16.200
Including you.

04:17.560 --> 04:18.360
So,

04:20.399 --> 04:21.680
about today,

04:23.960 --> 04:26.040
I was wrong. I'm sorry.

04:31.640 --> 04:34.560
I just didn't want everyone

04:34.560 --> 04:35.600
to hate me.

05:06.520 --> 05:07.280
Hello.

05:08.080 --> 05:09.340
Do you have time later?

05:10.600 --> 05:11.560
Can we meet?

05:36.680 --> 05:37.560
Xu Xiao,

05:39.920 --> 05:42.250
I still want to explain it to you in person.

05:42.360 --> 05:44.360
I really wasn't following you then.

05:44.960 --> 05:47.400
I only went because Xiaoxing said you were there.

05:47.400 --> 05:48.000
And then I...

05:48.000 --> 05:48.640
I know.

05:52.200 --> 05:54.330
I wasn't in a good mood that day either.

06:01.960 --> 06:03.520
Do you think someone

06:03.800 --> 06:04.960
could make a type of

06:04.960 --> 06:07.290
porcelain that puts people in a good mood?

06:09.240 --> 06:10.000
Actually,

06:11.200 --> 06:13.330
when you volunteered to team up today,

06:14.280 --> 06:15.540
I was quite surprised.

06:17.920 --> 06:18.640
After all,

06:20.520 --> 06:22.250
my attitude towards you before

06:22.640 --> 06:23.240
was so bad.

06:28.240 --> 06:28.680
I...

06:29.800 --> 06:30.480
I...

06:31.120 --> 06:33.360
I don't know what got into me today.

06:34.560 --> 06:35.760
I just raised my hand.

06:37.640 --> 06:39.300
Because at the time, I thought

06:40.040 --> 06:41.080
only at work

06:41.080 --> 06:42.360
would you talk to me.

06:44.240 --> 06:45.240
I don't want that.

06:50.080 --> 06:52.560
Because after coming to Jingdezhen,

06:53.560 --> 06:55.290
you're the first friend I made.

07:06.520 --> 07:07.280
First of all,

07:08.040 --> 07:10.500
I'm very grateful that you became my friend.

07:11.800 --> 07:14.600
My health hasn't been very good since I was a child.

07:14.680 --> 07:16.600
So my schooling was on and off.

07:17.040 --> 07:18.570
I didn't make many friends.

07:19.640 --> 07:21.240
After I came to Jingdezhen,

07:21.840 --> 07:23.280
I was really worried that I'd be alone

07:23.280 --> 07:24.560
just like before.

07:26.880 --> 07:28.960
So I really cherish our friendship.

07:30.400 --> 07:32.200
But I don't seem to be good at

07:32.680 --> 07:34.940
putting myself in other people's shoes.

07:35.600 --> 07:36.920
Including today,

07:37.920 --> 07:39.450
I also did something wrong.

07:39.480 --> 07:40.040
No.

07:41.920 --> 07:42.480
Xiaocen.

07:44.960 --> 07:45.960
Don't always put the blame

07:45.960 --> 07:47.040
on yourself.

07:49.680 --> 07:52.010
People who are willing to stay by your side

07:52.640 --> 07:54.200
won't leave you

07:55.480 --> 07:56.940
because of a small matter.

08:00.600 --> 08:01.200
Thank you.

08:05.040 --> 08:05.640
All right.

08:06.680 --> 08:07.210
Let's go.

08:08.440 --> 08:10.370
We still owe Mr. Yue an assignment.

08:11.200 --> 08:11.720
Okay.

08:14.360 --> 08:14.890
Let's go.

08:45.240 --> 08:45.720
Well...

08:48.920 --> 08:52.780
The person who tricked you into buying fake porcelain pieces that day

08:55.000 --> 08:55.600
was my dad.

09:10.880 --> 09:13.360
This is our university's graduate school.

09:13.520 --> 09:15.320
We have replica ancient wood-fired kilns

09:15.320 --> 09:17.580
and supporting production facilities.

09:18.240 --> 09:19.300
Everyone, come in.

09:20.800 --> 09:22.080
The production of ceramics

09:22.080 --> 09:24.160
goes through at least 72 processes,

09:24.520 --> 09:26.640
or even up to hundreds.

09:27.280 --> 09:29.280
Because our course time is limited,

09:29.320 --> 09:30.200
this time,

09:30.200 --> 09:32.920
we will skip the preliminary processes including clay selection, grinding,

09:32.920 --> 09:34.160
filtering, batching,

09:34.160 --> 09:35.840
moistening, and kneading.

09:36.480 --> 09:38.610
We will start directly from throwing.

10:13.160 --> 10:16.520
Now everyone's clay body is in a semi-dry state,

10:16.640 --> 10:18.440
suitable for the trimming step.

10:18.680 --> 10:20.960
That is, use the tools at hand

10:21.040 --> 10:22.840
to trim the vessel,

10:22.960 --> 10:24.720
making its surface smooth

10:24.720 --> 10:26.050
and thickness uniform.

10:27.840 --> 10:28.600
Look at this.

10:30.760 --> 10:32.800
Next is painting.

10:33.520 --> 10:35.520
First, draw a pattern on the clay body,

10:35.520 --> 10:37.520
and then color it with a liner brush.

10:37.600 --> 10:38.520
This stage

10:38.920 --> 10:40.520
is no longer unfamiliar to you.

10:40.520 --> 10:43.600
We already touched on this last time when we made Yuan blue-and-white porcelain.

10:43.600 --> 10:44.920
I hope everyone can

10:44.920 --> 10:46.400
do better than before.

11:02.400 --> 11:03.160
All right.

11:03.520 --> 11:04.680
Seal the kiln now.

11:06.680 --> 11:07.280
Students.

11:08.160 --> 11:09.160
Firing a wood kiln

11:09.320 --> 11:13.050
requires filling first, firing second, and extinguishing third.

11:13.080 --> 11:15.520
During the 30-hour firing process,

11:16.000 --> 11:17.080
when to raise the temperature

11:17.080 --> 11:18.200
and when to maintain it.

11:18.200 --> 11:19.330
When to add firewood

11:19.760 --> 11:21.960
requires the chief kiln master to be present at all times.

11:21.960 --> 11:24.080
They must constantly add firewood

11:24.360 --> 11:27.290
and observe the temperature of the kiln constantly.

11:42.160 --> 11:43.240
Recently,

11:43.320 --> 11:44.960
under Mr. Yue's guidance,

11:45.360 --> 11:48.290
we came to the traditional wood kiln production site

11:48.480 --> 11:50.480
and learned about ceramics making.

11:51.120 --> 11:52.520
It turns out just glazing

11:52.560 --> 11:54.080
has many methods.

11:54.800 --> 11:56.660
There are also many ways to glaze,

11:57.320 --> 11:58.650
including blow glazing

11:59.320 --> 12:00.360
and dip glazing.

12:02.320 --> 12:03.780
The pouring glaze method.

12:04.120 --> 12:06.400
After drying, it is put into the kiln

12:06.400 --> 12:08.680
and fired for up to 30 hours

12:09.080 --> 12:10.940
to produce exquisite porcelain.

12:11.880 --> 12:13.360
Traditional ceramics making

12:13.360 --> 12:14.840
involves 72 processes.

12:15.960 --> 12:17.560
Throwing and shaping.

12:20.000 --> 12:21.280
Trimming.

12:24.840 --> 12:26.080
Painting.

12:30.200 --> 12:30.960
Glazing.

12:36.160 --> 12:37.760
Overglaze painting.

12:40.760 --> 12:43.960
Finally, it is fired at a high temperature

12:44.680 --> 12:46.410
to become exquisite ceramics.

12:47.240 --> 12:49.360
Every process is indispensable.

12:50.200 --> 12:53.000
A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.

12:53.000 --> 12:54.440
The same goes for life.

12:59.280 --> 12:59.880
Class.

13:00.760 --> 13:03.040
This is Xu Xiao and Xiaocen's work.

13:03.240 --> 13:03.720
Not bad.

13:05.720 --> 13:08.080
Yan Xue and Wu Jing's work is also good.

13:08.880 --> 13:11.080
This is Yuexin's work, which is also not bad.

13:11.080 --> 13:11.640
Class,

13:12.160 --> 13:13.400
from your assignments,

13:13.400 --> 13:15.960
I saw your clumsiness and nervousness,

13:16.720 --> 13:18.250
but more importantly, I saw

13:18.560 --> 13:19.840
your earnestness

13:20.120 --> 13:21.200
and your wisdom.

13:22.680 --> 13:23.400
Now,

13:23.680 --> 13:25.760
I will talk to you about it.

13:28.080 --> 13:29.000
I finally found you.

13:29.000 --> 13:29.640
Who is this?

13:29.640 --> 13:30.200
Go.

13:30.200 --> 13:31.200
Stop. What are you doing?

13:31.200 --> 13:32.200
Come with me. Go, go.

13:32.200 --> 13:32.680
Let go!

13:32.680 --> 13:33.400
What are you doing?

13:33.400 --> 13:34.720
Let go! Let go!

13:34.800 --> 13:35.240
Let go!

13:35.720 --> 13:36.240
Let go!

13:37.080 --> 13:37.720
This is a classroom.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.280
Fine.

13:38.280 --> 13:39.240
What are you doing?

13:39.240 --> 13:40.040
Xu,

13:40.400 --> 13:42.120
you've got a backer, haven't you?

13:42.120 --> 13:43.280
You don't answer my calls.

13:43.280 --> 13:44.520
You don't go to the antique shop.

13:44.520 --> 13:45.600
Guilty conscience, right?

13:45.600 --> 13:46.730
Are you avoiding me?

13:47.000 --> 13:48.320
You know you're talking nonsense,

13:48.320 --> 13:49.760
and you can't take responsibility, right?

13:49.760 --> 13:50.640
Who's talking nonsense?

13:50.640 --> 13:51.160
You.

13:51.400 --> 13:53.000
Barging in here and making a scene like this

13:53.000 --> 13:55.160
is disrupting our normal teaching order.

13:55.160 --> 13:56.600
Please don't cause trouble here.

13:56.600 --> 13:58.000
He is your student, right?

13:58.000 --> 13:58.520
Yes.

13:58.720 --> 14:00.850
Can a student just talk nonsense here?

14:02.120 --> 14:02.960
Your student

14:03.120 --> 14:04.360
said our things

14:04.520 --> 14:05.320
are fake.

14:05.480 --> 14:07.480
But I found a master appraiser

14:07.520 --> 14:08.200
to take a look.

14:08.200 --> 14:08.960
It is real.

14:09.000 --> 14:09.800
What should we do?

14:09.800 --> 14:11.280
Can you take this responsibility?

14:11.280 --> 14:14.410
If you can't, the school will take full responsibility.

14:17.280 --> 14:18.040
Look.

14:18.520 --> 14:19.040
Look.

14:19.240 --> 14:20.320
Look carefully, everyone.

14:20.320 --> 14:21.580
Everyone, watch this.

14:21.600 --> 14:22.480
Sir,

14:22.520 --> 14:23.400
you inspect it.

14:23.640 --> 14:24.920
Inspect it yourself if you dare.

14:24.920 --> 14:26.320
Let's see if you tell the truth.

14:26.320 --> 14:26.760
Okay.

14:27.120 --> 14:27.640
You two,

14:28.680 --> 14:30.320
let's talk outside, alright?

14:30.320 --> 14:31.520
No, we'll stay right here.

14:31.520 --> 14:31.920
Right here.

14:31.920 --> 14:33.200
What? Afraid people will hear?

14:33.200 --> 14:34.640
Come, everyone, judge for yourselves.

14:34.640 --> 14:35.300
Okay, okay.

14:36.040 --> 14:37.240
A couple of days ago...

14:37.240 --> 14:39.320
My dad took this blue-and-white porcelain bowl

14:39.320 --> 14:40.560
to an antique shop.

14:41.320 --> 14:43.050
It's where he works part-time.

14:43.200 --> 14:45.360
He said our item was a fake.

14:45.520 --> 14:46.960
Is that true? Right?

14:46.960 --> 14:47.440
Yes.

14:47.440 --> 14:49.040
Just because of what he said,

14:49.320 --> 14:51.080
I smashed the porcelain bowl.

14:51.160 --> 14:53.240
Fortunately, I was careful at the time

14:53.240 --> 14:56.080
and brought back the bottom of my blue-and-white porcelain bowl.

14:56.080 --> 14:57.040
After going back,

14:57.040 --> 14:58.840
I was too angry to even swallow.

14:59.320 --> 15:01.320
We found another appraisal agency,

15:01.320 --> 15:04.200
and confirmed it's an authentic piece from the Chenghua reign.

15:04.200 --> 15:05.080
Your

15:05.240 --> 15:05.600
dad.

15:06.040 --> 15:07.840
You almost ruined me.

15:07.840 --> 15:08.640
Do you know that?

15:08.640 --> 15:09.880
How are you going to compensate me?

15:09.880 --> 15:10.540
Okay, okay.

15:10.680 --> 15:12.140
Please calm down, you two.

15:12.840 --> 15:14.120
What about the other pieces?

15:14.120 --> 15:16.000
I was lucky enough to get this piece back.

15:16.000 --> 15:17.400
I couldn't find the rest.

15:17.920 --> 15:18.280
Okay.

15:19.040 --> 15:20.320
May I take a look?

15:38.600 --> 15:39.080
Xu Xiao.

15:40.920 --> 15:42.180
Did you look at it then?

15:42.480 --> 15:42.960
I did,

15:43.720 --> 15:44.920
but I didn't touch it.

15:45.440 --> 15:46.600
It's an obvious fake.

15:46.600 --> 15:47.560
You little brat,

15:47.680 --> 15:48.240
you're still talking nonsense here.

15:48.240 --> 15:49.600
Stand back.

15:52.920 --> 15:53.720
Sir.

15:56.280 --> 15:57.120
This base

15:57.480 --> 15:58.800
looks real.

15:59.160 --> 15:59.720
But,

16:01.680 --> 16:03.520
it might be a composite.

16:03.800 --> 16:04.400
A composite?

16:04.400 --> 16:04.800
Yes.

16:05.800 --> 16:07.060
In porcelain forgery,

16:07.120 --> 16:08.520
the most important thing

16:08.520 --> 16:11.000
is mixing old and new pieces.

16:11.080 --> 16:13.080
They use an old piece as a base,

16:13.120 --> 16:15.880
and add newly fired pieces on top.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.120
At the seams,

16:17.120 --> 16:20.080
they carefully cover it with glaze.

16:20.120 --> 16:21.920
This is highly deceptive.

16:22.200 --> 16:23.160
You mean

16:24.160 --> 16:25.800
our old man got scammed?

16:25.840 --> 16:26.840
It's possible.

16:27.360 --> 16:29.040
You're protecting your student

16:29.040 --> 16:30.700
and lying through your teeth.

16:30.920 --> 16:32.000
Please calm down.

16:33.720 --> 16:34.520
Gentlemen,

16:35.000 --> 16:36.400
we will find the evidence

16:36.800 --> 16:38.800
and give you a satisfactory answer.

16:39.120 --> 16:39.680
Fine.

16:40.800 --> 16:42.240
A satisfactory answer.

16:45.280 --> 16:46.610
A satisfactory answer.

16:48.160 --> 16:49.200
A satisfactory answer.

16:49.200 --> 16:49.640
Dad!

16:51.480 --> 16:51.840
Dad!

16:51.960 --> 16:52.920
Answer.

16:54.160 --> 16:54.920
Answer.

16:55.320 --> 16:55.840
Answer.

16:55.840 --> 16:56.160
You.

16:56.160 --> 16:56.890
My homework.

16:58.960 --> 16:59.840
Answer.

16:59.840 --> 17:00.320
You.

17:00.720 --> 17:01.640
What are you doing?

17:01.640 --> 17:02.280
What?

17:02.280 --> 17:04.079
Stop it. Don't smash it.

17:04.079 --> 17:05.800
Stop it.

17:05.800 --> 17:06.760
Call the police.

17:10.480 --> 17:10.920
Dad.

17:12.240 --> 17:13.040
What's wrong?

17:13.200 --> 17:13.640
Dad.

17:18.400 --> 17:19.240
You.

17:20.040 --> 17:21.560
Just your word.

17:23.280 --> 17:24.680
300,000 is gone.

17:24.680 --> 17:25.560
300,000.

17:25.560 --> 17:25.920
Dad.

17:26.000 --> 17:28.400
You have to give me an explanation for this.

17:28.400 --> 17:29.480
Dad, Dad.

17:29.520 --> 17:30.320
What's wrong?

17:31.080 --> 17:33.210
Take him to the hospital immediately.

17:35.920 --> 17:36.780
It's like this.

17:36.960 --> 17:38.220
I was teaching a class.

17:38.280 --> 17:40.240
Today is the students' assignment exhibition,

17:40.240 --> 17:41.320
which is displayed right here.

17:41.320 --> 17:42.040
Then they

17:42.040 --> 17:43.700
suddenly barged in from here.

17:43.960 --> 17:46.400
This old man bought a piece of porcelain at a porcelain shop.

17:46.400 --> 17:48.080
Xu Xiao said it might be fake.

17:48.520 --> 17:50.160
So they came looking for Xu Xiao now.

17:50.160 --> 17:50.800
Getting so excited...

17:50.800 --> 17:52.280
He smashed his classmate's assignment.

17:52.280 --> 17:55.080
Look at these porcelain shards all over the floor.

18:07.480 --> 18:08.680
Strictly speaking,

18:09.440 --> 18:12.840
the school does not oppose college students working part-time.

18:12.840 --> 18:15.040
However, elevating personal opinions

18:15.520 --> 18:17.850
to the level of cultural relics appraisal

18:17.920 --> 18:20.760
definitely goes beyond the scope of a student.

18:21.080 --> 18:21.760
Principal,

18:21.960 --> 18:22.560
Xu Xiao

18:22.560 --> 18:24.360
just expressed his own opinion.

18:24.720 --> 18:26.640
At most, it's just a reference.

18:26.840 --> 18:27.400
Besides,

18:27.960 --> 18:29.400
they smashed the bowl themselves,

18:29.400 --> 18:31.520
and now they regret it and come to make a scene at school.

18:31.520 --> 18:32.600
Isn't that ridiculous?

18:32.600 --> 18:33.530
Yes, Principal.

18:33.720 --> 18:34.240
But

18:34.960 --> 18:37.290
if they keep making a fuss with the school,

18:37.640 --> 18:38.970
the impact on the school

18:40.480 --> 18:42.000
will still be significant.

18:42.000 --> 18:42.660
Principal,

18:43.520 --> 18:45.600
if we punish Xu Xiao for this,

18:46.240 --> 18:47.840
wouldn't it indirectly

18:48.200 --> 18:49.320
mean admitting that

18:49.320 --> 18:50.000
the school

18:50.480 --> 18:52.080
thinks the student is wrong?

18:52.960 --> 18:53.760
Let's do this.

18:54.160 --> 18:55.280
Since it's pending,

18:55.280 --> 18:57.080
let's continue investigating.

18:57.120 --> 18:58.520
Out of responsibility,

18:58.920 --> 18:59.640
the school

19:00.000 --> 19:02.320
really needs to notify the parents.

19:02.960 --> 19:03.560
Mr. Liang,

19:04.200 --> 19:05.600
you are in charge of this.

19:06.720 --> 19:07.160
Okay.

19:11.040 --> 19:11.640
Tip-off.

19:11.880 --> 19:14.240
The school has decided not to punish Xu Xiao for now.

19:14.240 --> 19:14.720
But

19:14.840 --> 19:16.120
they will call his parents.

19:16.120 --> 19:17.920
Then everything should be fine.

19:17.920 --> 19:19.200
After all, the school is involved.

19:19.200 --> 19:21.200
Zhang Jiatian can't just use force.

19:21.440 --> 19:23.280
I have something to do...

19:24.480 --> 19:27.140
Are you feeling sorry for the broken porcelain?

19:27.320 --> 19:29.320
Couldn't he have some common sense?

19:29.320 --> 19:31.680
Every piece of porcelain had a name marked under it.

19:31.680 --> 19:33.320
If he wanted to smash them, he should've been more accurate.

19:33.320 --> 19:34.160
What do you know?

19:34.160 --> 19:36.090
This is an indiscriminate attack.

19:36.520 --> 19:37.760
Looking at his attitude,

19:37.760 --> 19:40.200
I believe he's the type to smash his own porcelain bowl.

19:40.200 --> 19:42.260
Smashing anyone's is unacceptable.

19:43.440 --> 19:45.520
I originally planned that after this exhibition,

19:45.520 --> 19:47.380
I would keep my work as a souvenir.

19:53.200 --> 19:54.640
We've all worked hard for days.

19:54.640 --> 19:56.970
How about we go get some food to celebrate?

19:57.120 --> 19:57.760
My treat.

19:58.520 --> 19:59.760
Then let's hurry up.

20:00.160 --> 20:00.840
Since I heard it,

20:00.840 --> 20:01.280
I'm going too.

20:01.280 --> 20:01.680
I'm going too.

20:01.680 --> 20:02.640
Once you hear it's the class monitor's treat,

20:02.640 --> 20:04.240
everyone wants to go, right?

20:04.400 --> 20:05.640
We didn't say we wouldn't take you two.

20:05.640 --> 20:07.240
Let's go and see what to eat.

20:08.400 --> 20:09.120
Xu Xiao.

20:11.440 --> 20:12.080
I'm sorry.

20:13.120 --> 20:13.920
Because of me,

20:15.200 --> 20:16.920
the porcelain you worked so hard on was smashed.

20:16.920 --> 20:18.200
It's obviously their fault.

20:18.200 --> 20:19.080
You don't need to apologize.

20:19.080 --> 20:20.000
Let's go eat together.

20:20.000 --> 20:21.680
Yeah, let's have some good food.

20:21.680 --> 20:22.080
Let's go together

20:22.080 --> 20:24.040
and put all your worries behind you.

20:24.040 --> 20:24.700
No, thanks.

20:25.040 --> 20:26.240
I'll head back first.

20:37.280 --> 20:38.760
What did I tell you?

20:39.320 --> 20:41.650
He shouldn't have applied to this school.

20:41.800 --> 20:43.400
You insisted that the child has grown up

20:43.400 --> 20:45.460
and we should respect his interests.

20:45.720 --> 20:46.780
What's the result?

20:46.880 --> 20:48.240
He is still a student,

20:48.280 --> 20:49.840
yet he has caused such big trouble.

20:49.840 --> 20:51.680
What will happen when he grows up?

20:51.680 --> 20:54.340
The school didn't say it's our child's problem.

20:54.480 --> 20:56.040
Why wouldn't it be him?

20:56.960 --> 20:59.000
How obsessed he is with those bottles and jars,

20:59.000 --> 21:00.200
you know very well.

21:00.200 --> 21:00.640
No.

21:01.080 --> 21:02.440
The child likes to study.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.360
That's a good thing.

21:03.360 --> 21:04.960
If he studies this field,

21:05.600 --> 21:08.240
who can guarantee he won't make mistakes in his life?

21:08.240 --> 21:10.570
Who can guarantee he won't offend people?

21:11.680 --> 21:13.320
Over the years around us,

21:13.760 --> 21:15.720
there are many people whose families are ruined.

21:15.720 --> 21:17.720
I am a living example.

21:18.240 --> 21:19.640
Every year in this market,

21:19.640 --> 21:22.300
how many people have their reputations ruined?

21:22.640 --> 21:24.400
The old one is already crazy,

21:24.680 --> 21:25.880
and now the young one.

21:28.200 --> 21:29.130
This profession

21:29.280 --> 21:30.520
really harms people.

21:31.440 --> 21:33.240
I really don't know why he,

21:33.480 --> 21:34.880
he takes after Xu Jinsong.

21:34.880 --> 21:35.680
Say a few words less.

21:35.680 --> 21:36.760
Being influenced by him

21:36.760 --> 21:38.040
to ignore his proper duties.

21:38.040 --> 21:39.320
Okay, drink some water.

21:39.320 --> 21:40.520
He was still young then.

21:40.520 --> 21:41.120
Yes, yes.

21:41.120 --> 21:42.560
He definitely doesn't know

21:42.560 --> 21:45.420
the feeling of our family being forced to pay debts.

22:03.560 --> 22:04.490
I'm telling you,

22:04.600 --> 22:05.730
I won't divorce you.

22:06.000 --> 22:08.200
And I definitely won't give you our son.

22:21.760 --> 22:22.960
Hey everyone,

22:23.440 --> 22:24.240
look at this.

22:24.880 --> 22:25.600
Look.

22:26.280 --> 22:27.120
What is this?

22:27.360 --> 22:28.160
What's going on?

22:28.160 --> 22:29.120
This is the guy causing trouble for Xu Xiao.

22:29.120 --> 22:30.250
Let's go take a look.

22:30.560 --> 22:31.220
That's him.

22:31.600 --> 22:32.460
It's him again.

22:32.880 --> 22:34.760
I hope he's not looking for trouble with our class.

22:34.760 --> 22:36.120
Looks like he's live streaming.

22:36.120 --> 22:37.160
Xu Jinsong.

22:37.400 --> 22:39.280
This guy used his

22:39.280 --> 22:41.080
cultural relics restoration skills back then

22:41.080 --> 22:45.040
to buy a fake Ming Chenghua porcelain at a low price.

22:45.200 --> 22:46.800
Then he repackaged it

22:46.960 --> 22:50.090
and sold it to a buyer at the high price of a genuine piece.

22:50.120 --> 22:51.120
Then this buyer

22:51.160 --> 22:53.120
found an expert to appraise it later.

22:53.120 --> 22:54.880
It turned out to be a fake.

22:54.880 --> 22:55.640
What kind of person is he?

22:55.640 --> 22:57.640
What kind of good son could he raise?

22:57.680 --> 22:59.520
And he says our things are fake.

22:59.600 --> 23:00.840
Who are you?

23:01.560 --> 23:02.280
Come, come, come.

23:02.280 --> 23:03.320
That's him. That's him.

23:03.320 --> 23:04.520
He is Xu Jinsong's son.

23:04.520 --> 23:04.840
Don't move.

23:04.840 --> 23:05.360
Xu Xiao.

23:05.360 --> 23:06.240
I've already explained this.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.040
Stop being unreasonable.

23:07.040 --> 23:08.100
Me, unreasonable?

23:08.120 --> 23:09.240
Look, that's him.

23:09.240 --> 23:09.960
He is Xu Xiao.

23:09.960 --> 23:10.360
Get out of the way.

23:10.360 --> 23:11.360
Watch your mouth.

23:11.400 --> 23:11.840
Stop fighting.

23:11.840 --> 23:12.640
I'll call the police if you keep this up.

23:12.640 --> 23:13.400
I'm calling the police.

23:13.400 --> 23:14.600
This is our school gate.

23:14.600 --> 23:15.600
Get out of the way.

23:22.560 --> 23:23.890
Do you have time to talk?

23:28.000 --> 23:28.600
Xu Xiao.

23:29.920 --> 23:32.400
It's no use letting this matter drag on.

23:32.920 --> 23:34.850
I've already contacted Mr. Zhang.

23:34.880 --> 23:35.960
He hopes you

23:36.800 --> 23:38.200
can apologize in person.

23:40.240 --> 23:42.120
I did nothing wrong. Why should I apologize?

23:42.120 --> 23:43.640
Don't rush to explain.

23:43.920 --> 23:46.050
It's not about right or wrong anymore.

23:47.200 --> 23:47.800
That guy,

23:48.280 --> 23:49.800
his scandals have been dug up,

23:49.800 --> 23:51.530
and it's causing a huge uproar.

23:51.760 --> 23:54.020
This involves more than just you and him.

23:54.280 --> 23:55.440
It also involves your school,

23:55.440 --> 23:57.160
and Mr. Yue, you know?

23:58.120 --> 23:59.840
Your uncle and I have discussed it.

23:59.840 --> 24:01.160
We are willing to pay 300,000

24:01.160 --> 24:02.200
to settle this.

24:02.400 --> 24:04.060
Then we can put this behind us.

24:06.080 --> 24:07.210
But the condition is

24:08.160 --> 24:10.020
you have to suspend your studies.

24:11.600 --> 24:13.040
Why do I have to suspend my studies?

24:13.040 --> 24:13.440
You...

24:13.640 --> 24:14.960
Suspending his studies

24:14.960 --> 24:16.420
affects the kid's future.

24:16.840 --> 24:19.170
You need to ask for his own opinion on this.

24:19.480 --> 24:21.080
Can you stop talking?

24:21.480 --> 24:23.120
I don't want Xu Xiao to have

24:23.120 --> 24:24.160
anything to do with this industry anymore.

24:24.160 --> 24:24.920
Okay, okay.

24:27.680 --> 24:29.210
I won't suspend my studies.

24:30.160 --> 24:31.600
And I won't apologize either.

24:31.600 --> 24:32.600
Stop right there.

24:34.280 --> 24:36.340
Have you considered Mom's feelings?

24:37.360 --> 24:39.960
I worked so hard to get away from everything in the past.

24:39.960 --> 24:42.220
Now you want to drag me back to square one.

24:49.600 --> 24:51.330
Let me think about it some more.

24:52.400 --> 24:52.600
You...

24:52.600 --> 24:52.920
Right, right, right.

24:52.920 --> 24:54.280
Think about it.

24:56.280 --> 24:56.680
He...

24:57.280 --> 24:57.960
Stop talking.
